unban.description: This command will unban the user provided.

warn.example: warn @soos creating the best discord bot there is.
warn.description: Will DM the provided user the provided warning. As of now, there is no warn tracking.

purge.description: This command will delete the # of messages given from that channel.

kick.description: This command will kick the user provided with the reason provided.

ban.description: This command will ban the user provided with the reason provided.

prefix.description: This command will change soosBot's prefix. Mention soosBot to view its current prefix.
